{"type": "article", "id": 7585, "title": "Abie Abdillah 藤条桌椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-20T07:32:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234757mXfihgRCkD9rKpOI.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t来自设计工作室 Studiohiji 的印尼籍设计师 Abie Abdillah 一直对于藤条家具有着热爱和研究，这次他在新加坡推出了一系列藤条桌椅。这些桌椅由手工编织完成，看似柔软的藤条经过编织可以形成稳固的椅子。设计师试图通过这一组作品唤起人们对于藤条材料的关注和喜爱。这款椅子有多种颜色可选，和浅色的藤条呼应，看起来活泼又简洁。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234754SgrHIx2bpqDJaeN3.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.62037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234755KsMVc9Ugqk40TL3a.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.55185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234755GutCa3RV61mITSjb.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.6712963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234755rnUP80tkNDIBhSTf.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.63425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234756jwtI8r72gCNpSckX.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.65833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}